for example:

```
function foo {
  param(
    [unionType('string','System.Management.Automation.PSModuleInfo')]
   [parameter(valuefrompipeline)]
    $module
  )
  proceess {

     # code
  }
}

```
works in all caases 


```
PS>  get-module mymodule | foo
PS> foo -module  mymodule
PS> 'mymddule'  |  foo
```


this feature is not to replace  paramsets or argument transformer but its more easy less typing...etc

